{"1":[[1710,1822,"Hi."],[1822,1889,"You’re hurt."],[1889,1972,"No."],[1972,2202,"I’m not hurt, okay?"],[2202,2548,"And even if I was, it'd be a good thing."],[2602,2798,"Because then I’d get to see my Dr. Charlie."],[3007,3215,"I got you something."],[3745,3924,"This is too much."],[3924,4104,"Your salary isn't much to begin with."],[4104,4233,"You really shouldn't have."],[4254,4662,"Well, as a Private,"],[4662,4900,"this is what I can afford."],[5063,5159,"But I wanted to."],[5355,5547,"I really love it, Private Harry."],[5593,5689,"You know, Dr. Charlie"],[5689,5776,"I have to tell you something."],[5901,6147,"I'm not just a Private,"],[6147,6348,"I'm also -"],[6348,6489,"I'm sorry, there's an emergency."],[6489,6585,"I have to go."],[6585,6673,"Can we talk about this later?"],[6723,6940,"The truth is, I'm a Prince,"],[6940,7198,"and this is just my royal military duty."],[7978,8204,"Harry, I have a surprise for you."],[8204,8408,"Charlie, hurry!"],[8408,8596,"Your mom has been admitted to the ICU."],[8996,9171,"End stage heart failure."],[9184,9359,"She needs a transplant."],[9359,9559,"Okay, you're a doctor."],[9559,9663,"You know this surgery can cost"],[9663,9868,"half a million dollars easily."],[9868,10135,"And that's if they can find a matching donor."],[10201,10422,"No matter what, I will save her."],[10422,10618,"Okay, then call Harry."],[10618,10706,"You both need to come up"],[10706,10806,"with the money together."],[10806,11098,"No, don't tell him."],[11098,11286,"Harry's just a regular soldier."],[11286,11398,"He doesn't have that kind of money."],[11398,11569,"Yeah, but he is your boyfriend."],[11569,11757,"I'll figure it out myself."],[11874,12012,"I really think you should tell him."],[12012,12233,"Please, Gavin."],[12474,12579,"Fine."],[13046,13092,"Alright."],[13092,13179,"How are you gonna start this?"],[13179,13442,"Are you gonna get down on one knee?"],[13475,13655,"No, no, no."],[13655,13817,"You’re going to tell the truth first, right?"],[13817,14022,"She still doesn’t know that you're a Prince."],[14022,14255,"You have to -"],[14255,14418,"No."],[14885,14969,"So,"],[14969,15277,"compared to your Soldier boyfriend,"],[15277,15486,"who’s better?"],[15486,15719,"You, of course."],[15719,15911,"He's all muscle, but,"],[15911,15999,"not much good in bed."],[15999,16066,"not much good in bed."],[16253,16403,"Charlie!"]],"2":[[0,171,"Charlie?"],[725,946,"You know, I think you owe me an explanation."],[1017,1209,"There's nothing to explain."],[1209,1459,"This is exactly what it looks like."],[2740,2965,"Why lie to him like this?"],[2965,3157,"He doesn't even know that you're pregnant."],[3311,3482,"It's better this way."],[3933,4045,"Harry,"],[4045,4187,"I’m sorry."],[4187,4346,"I can't drag you into this."],[5000,5109,"Vincent, I'm the best doctor"],[5109,5288,"in this entire hospital."],[5288,5559,"Why am I not on the consultation list again?"],[5680,5722,"Look."],[5722,5818,"Look."],[5818,5943,"My hands are tied."],[5943,6243,"There's limited spots available and,"],[6243,6381,"between you and me,"],[6381,6464,"when the daughter"],[6464,6602,"of the owner of this hospital -"],[6602,6902,"I've been waiting for this for three years."],[8087,8258,"Well,"],[8258,8495,"I suppose there might be other ways."],[8521,8700,"Vincent, I'm a mother."],[8700,9013,"And? I don't mind."],[9013,9138,"I mean, I’m not the Dad."],[9505,9738,"Be professional."],[9818,9955,"You know,"],[9955,10197,"everyone in this entire hospital"],[10197,10431,"knows that you have pregnant."],[10431,10685,"And you won't even say who the dad is."],[10685,10952,"And here you want to go acting all"],[10952,11152,"holier than thou."],[11252,11411,"We interrupt our regularly"],[11411,11686,"scheduled programing for this special report."],[11740,11957,"His Royal Highness Prince Harry"],[11957,12070,"will serve on behalf"],[12070,12387,"of the Royal Family again, after five years."],[12491,12620,"Deploying to Troy"],[12620,12766,"to join the peacekeeping forces."],[13088,13329,"It's been five years, Harry."]],"3":[[33,196,"I only found out you were a Prince"],[196,392,"after we had broken up."],[392,521,"How could you lie to me"],[521,692,"when I was the one worried about dragging"],[692,829,"you down?"],[909,980,"Hold on."],[1001,1155,"You're not telling me that His Royal"],[1155,1413,"Highness himself is your baby's father?"],[1413,1601,"At least he's not a piece of shit like you."],[1601,1647,"Hey!"],[1739,1864,"Watch how you're talking to me."],[1922,2039,"You seem to forget that your Mom"],[2039,2185,"is a patient here."],[2185,2377,"And what about all of those medical bills"],[2377,2698,"that you never paid, and I let it slide?"],[2698,3111,"Wonder what would happen if all of a sudden"],[3111,3432,"I ordered them to just stop her treatment?"],[3495,3628,"Are you threatening me?"],[3628,3703,"Maybe."],[3703,3874,"Okay,"],[3874,4074,"then I guess I'll just tell everyone"],[4074,4225,"about what you just did."],[4225,4341,"All of those medical bills"],[4341,4475,"that you never paid,"],[4475,4696,"and I let it slide."],[4696,4875,"If you wanna play that game."],[4875,4996,"How about"],[4996,5113,"you go and join the medics"],[5113,5330,"on the battlefield at Troy?"],[5359,5430,"How do you like that"],[5430,5563,"for your new assignment?"],[5584,5672,"Harry,"],[5672,5851,"are we going to meet again?"],[7294,7386,"I was reading the list of names"],[7386,7565,"I was reading the list of names"],[7565,7716,"for the new medics,"],[7716,7824,"I saw a Charlie."],[7957,8158,"Couldn't be the Charlie that we know?"],[8158,8270,"I don't know a Charlie."],[8270,8412,"You're right."],[8412,8554,"We don't know a Charlie."],[8587,8675,"Your Highness."],[8675,8771,"You're heading back to the frontlines"],[8771,9004,"after five years."],[9004,9184,"Wouldn’t have anything to do with Dr. Charlie,"],[9184,9300,"would it?"],[9300,9509,"Like I said,"],[9509,9713,"I don't know a Charlie."],[9989,10126,"Your Highness."],[10126,10377,"Look! Isn't that Dr. Charlie?"]],"4":[[875,1109,"Thank you for taking care of Nick, Gavin."],[1109,1305,"Oh, please."],[1430,1580,"As long as you introduce me to that"],[1580,1730,"hot guy nurse of yours."],[1730,1830,"I will."],[1830,2014,"Just please keep taking care of Nick"],[2014,2173,"while I'm here on my Troy assignment."],[2185,2373,"Why don't you just quit?"],[2373,2535,"I mean, Vincent's always giving you"],[2535,2631,"a hard time."],[2631,2727,"No."],[2727,3011,"My Mom, her medical bills, and Nick."],[3011,3140,"They both need me."],[3307,3449,"Say hi."],[3449,3549,"Hi."],[3549,3774,"Mommy, when are you going to be home?"],[3774,3903,"I miss you."],[3903,4037,"Soon, Nicky."],[4037,4162,"But for now, you're going to have to listen"],[4162,4291,"to Uncle Gavin, okay?"],[4325,4404,"Okay."],[4404,4746,"Uncle Gavin said you're going to look for dad."],[4746,4896,"When am I going to meet him?"],[5021,5326,"Nick, why don't you go play for a little bit, okay?"],[5326,5505,"I told you not to tell him about Harry."],[5505,5830,"I'm sorry, okay? It just seems so unfair."],[5830,6135,"Why can't you just tell Harry that Nick is his?"],[6135,6272,"I can't."],[6272,6431,"I don't deserve his help."],[6431,6598,"We literally faked it!"],[6598,6694,"Just tell him."],[6694,6986,"No, no, I made my choice."],[6986,7219,"And besides, he never told me who he was"],[7219,7403,"five years ago, so he probably didn't"],[7403,7524,"even really love me anyway."],[7524,7753,"But Nick should have a dad."],[7753,7870,"I can raise him by myself."],[9351,9442,"No way."],[9442,9743,"Prince Harry's here to greet us himself."],[10085,10239,"Prince Harry."],[10239,10372,"It's been a minute."]],"5":[[1568,1772,"Doc! He's been shot."],[1797,1910,"Please!"],[1910,2177,"Ow! Let me go."],[3032,3186,"That does seem painful."],[4391,4579,"I thought that people in your line of work"],[4579,4767,"were used to getting hurt."],[5025,5230,"Dr. Charlie, you don't,"],[5230,5455,"you don’t treat gang members?"],[5659,5822,"I'm a doctor,"],[5822,6018,"so saving lives is my duty"],[6018,6222,"no matter who walks through my doors."],[6222,6448,"Doc, we're not gangsters."],[6448,6573,"We’re soldiers on leave."],[6635,6715,"You’re soldiers?"],[6715,6923,"We were on our way to a wedding"],[6923,7140,"for a retired guy"],[7140,7440,"and some gangsters seeking revenge."],[7440,7540,"Luckily, we're all still alive."],[7636,7720,"I'm sorry."],[7720,7899,"It's my mistake."],[8604,8717,"You'll be fine."],[8717,8883,"You just need to keep it dry"],[8883,9071,"and disinfect it regularly."],[9071,9125,"Okay."],[9334,9488,"Dr. Charlie,"],[9488,9680,"you know, you really hurt my"],[9680,9868,"feelings there with your judgment."],[9868,10114,"Do you think that you could help"],[10114,10251,"clean my wound a couple more times?"],[10422,10568,"The nurse will take care of that."],[10568,10869,"No no no, I,"],[10960,11236,"I, I only want you to do it."],[11720,11995,"Okay, I’ll take that as a yes."],[12804,12958,"Come back in three days."],[13113,13238,"Dr. Charlie?"],[13238,13463,"You know, I know you must be pretty busy as"],[13463,13626,"an ER doctor,"],[13626,13984,"so you probably don't have a boyfriend, right?"],[14043,14255,"You probably live a very dangerous"],[14255,14401,"life in the army,"],[14401,14914,"so, no girlfriend, right?"],[17817,17997,"It's been five years."],[17997,18147,"Do you still hate me?"]],"6":[[41,179,"Dr. Charlie?"],[179,383,"Do you and Prince Harry know each other?"],[383,462,"No."],[513,688,"I heard he joined the peacekeeping forces"],[688,900,"as a civilian five years ago."],[900,1046,"Yeah, he got shot, too."],[1046,1142,"How do you know?"],[1217,1401,"I just heard it from someone."],[1401,1518,"Weird."],[1518,1701,"Why is he back all of a sudden?"],[1772,1939,"Maybe because of Lady Selina."],[1997,2068,"Selina?"],[2068,2173,"You haven't heard?"],[2173,2293,"It's his fiancée."],[2318,2452,"Fiancée?"],[3094,3199,"Am I late?"],[3399,3524,"I was at a gala."],[3828,3953,"I'm Selina,"],[3953,4250,"and I will be in charge of the medic's operations."],[4250,4567,"Selina? She's Duke Ford's daughter."],[4567,4725,"She's on the front lines with us."],[4725,4842,"You didn't know?"],[4842,5084,"Lady Selina is engaged to Prince Harry."],[5084,5359,"Oh, so that's why he's back, it's for her."],[5359,5605,"Aw, that's so romantic."],[5605,5764,"Come on, ladies."],[5764,6010,"I am here to work."],[6268,6431,"You've moved on."],[6431,6614,"I guess that's it for us."]],"7":[[1238,1397,"All right, ladies."],[1397,1539,"Our first task will be to"],[1539,1730,"administer physical exams"],[1730,2027,"among our soldiers."],[2364,2473,"Who will be so lucky"],[2473,2627,"to do Prince Harry's?"],[2627,2823,"You think Selina wouldn't do his personally?"],[2823,2998,"Please."],[3616,3737,"Please undress and get on the bed,"],[3737,3791,"Your Highness."],[3841,4016,"Shouldn't Dr. Charlie be quite familiar"],[4016,4229,"with my body by now?"],[4650,4896,"I don't know what you mean, Your Highness."],[4896,5017,"I'm just a doctor."],[5017,5238,"Well, unfortunately, I don't like women"],[5238,5497,"that I don't know seeing me naked."],[5547,5651,"Wait, are you hurt?"],[5651,5693,"Can I take a look?"],[5759,5834,"I'm sorry,"],[5834,6047,"did Dr. Charlie only start caring about me"],[6047,6318,"when she found out who I really was?"],[6318,6544,"A little too late, don't you think?"],[6544,6731,"I'm just doing my job."],[6731,6881,"Well, don't."],[6881,7086,"Because I'll have somebody else look at it."],[7599,7816,"Good thing I didn't tell him about Nick."],[7816,8033,"It's really over between us."],[9046,9200,"Hey!"],[9200,9471,"I have some candy for you guys."],[9471,9555,"Here!"],[9555,9855,"Thank you! -You're welcome."],[10631,10789,"Help!"],[10789,10994,"Is there anybody here?"],[11257,11353,"Boss."],[11394,11624,"I think I know you well enough to guess"],[11624,11849,"that you came back for Dr. Charlie?"],[11891,12066,"What happened five years ago?"],[12066,12195,"You two were so happy."],[12341,12637,"She's not a girl that I can trust."],[12637,12712,"It's done."],[12729,12775,"But -"],[12775,12883,"There you are,"],[12883,12992,"Your Highness."],[13079,13179,"What do you need?"],[13179,13450,"Well, if you wouldn't mind giving me a"],[13450,13638,"tour of the camp so I can see"],[13638,13780,"what I need to work on."],[13813,14047,"What you need to work on is your outfits."],[14126,14297,"This is a war zone,"],[14297,14368,"not a gala."],[14647,14739,"Your Highness,"],[14739,14906,"Dr. Charlie stepped on a landmine."]],"8":[[41,175,"Daisy?"],[175,296,"Daisy, did you send someone?"],[296,425,"Dr. Charlie."],[471,642,"Did you not read the sign?"],[642,813,"I just wanted to give the kids some candy."],[813,896,"I didn't think there was"],[896,980,"going to be landmines."],[980,1142,"You know, ignorance is not an excuse"],[1142,1280,"for disobeying the rules."],[1280,1568,"Can you please help me get out of here?"],[2060,2185,"Why would I do that?"],[2185,2385,"No. Nick and Mom need me."],[2385,2485,"I can't die."],[2485,2773,"Please, if you're able to."],[2773,2882,"I can't die here."],[3157,3244,"Okay, move your foot."],[3244,3307,"What?"],[3307,3536,"You have to get off so I can get on."],[3536,3753,"You can step on it without it exploding?"],[3753,3953,"Actually not."],[3953,4079,"But if you want to live,"],[4079,4241,"then I guess I'll just die in your place."],[4241,4475,"No. I'm not letting you die."],[4475,4621,"Call the bomb disposal people."],[4621,4704,"Come on!"],[4704,4783,"Go!"],[5972,6135,"We didn't blow up."],[6260,6594,"Dr. Charlie, please be professional."],[6735,6890,"Why did you lie to me?"],[6890,7082,"You didn't even tell me that you were a Prince."],[7082,7165,"Five years ago."],[7165,7365,"I came to tell you"],[7365,7603,"when I was going to propose to you."],[7603,7903,"Obviously that wasn't necessary."],[8041,8195,"Why did you do that to me?"],[8195,8312,"Harry."],[8312,8612,"What happened five years ago was not -"],[8975,9121,"Mommy, I miss you."],[9384,9530,"Who's this?"],[9530,9638,"Is this Daddy?"],[9638,9738,"Is that kid mine?"]],"9":[[0,125,"Nick."],[125,266,"Has Mommy picked up?"],[266,479,"So the kid is his?"],[571,696,"You know what?"],[696,888,"That's my bad, Dr. Charlie."],[888,1026,"You know, it looks like the last five years"],[1026,1234,"were really great for you."],[1234,1447,"Congratulations."],[1701,1910,"Wait, was that Harry?"],[1956,2047,"Yeah."],[2047,2198,"Is he being a jerk about what happened"],[2198,2327,"five years ago again?"],[2419,2648,"No, he actually just saved me."],[2648,2752,"He wasn't."],[2773,2977,"Does he know that Nick is his?"],[3119,3332,"I didn't tell him."],[3670,3941,"Harry's the father of Charlie's child?"],[3941,4087,"How could this be?"],[4087,4396,"And five years ago."],[5405,5559,"Why didn’t they get married,"],[5559,5759,"even though they had a child together?"],[5889,6018,"Does that mean that Gavin"],[6018,6247,"is not the father?"],[6531,6652,"Harry."],[6694,6911,"You're working too hard."],[6911,7040,"I made you coffee."],[7111,7353,"Thank you."],[7657,7941,"Harry, you already knew Dr. Charlie"],[7941,8162,"before coming here, right?"],[8162,8291,"No."],[8362,8554,"I must be mistaken then."],[8554,8708,"I just saw the two of you chatting."],[8775,9054,"I heard she has an adorable son."],[9054,9317,"She must be really happy at home."],[9417,9630,"You know, I have"],[9630,9768,"a lot of work that I have to do."],[9768,9901,"Please excuse me."],[10710,10756,"I guess"],[10756,11173,"he still doesn't know that the child is his."],[11173,11344,"Charlie, I don't care what happened"],[11344,11603,"between you two five years ago,"],[11603,11799,"Harry's mine."]],"10":[[158,283,"Hey, guys."],[283,375,"Where's Tommy?"],[375,592,"We haven't seen him today."],[592,675,"That’s weird."],[675,946,"Thank you, thank you."],[1418,1526,"Sir."],[1526,1739,"Dr. Charlie is kidnapped by local criminals."],[1739,1835,"We have to go rescue her."],[1835,1893,"No."],[1893,2173,"No, our military has gotten involved already."],[2248,2381,"They’re confident that they will have"],[2381,2556,"a rescue within 24 hours."],[2556,2702,"You stay put."],[2702,2844,"I can't."],[2844,2936,"The longer that we wait,"],[2936,3199,"the more danger she's going to get into."],[3261,3340,"I'm going."],[3407,3636,"But, Harry, you're the Prince."],[3636,3812,"You are the heir to the throne."],[3812,4133,"You can't go risk your life for a doctor."],[4133,4320,"Charlie is not just a doctor."],[4387,4521,"She is a citizen of this country"],[4521,4654,"and as royalty, I have a duty to"],[4654,4771,"protect my citizens."],[4813,5134,"But they're probably terrorists."],[5134,5276,"You could die."],[5276,5476,"I am a soldier."],[5476,5622,"I am prepared to lay down my life"],[5622,5797,"for my country and its citizens."],[5805,6026,"No but,"],[6026,6310,"Your Majesty, you cannot let him do this."],[6310,6514,"Three hours."],[6514,6902,"You have three hours to be a regular soldier."],[6923,7115,"I will turn a blind eye."],[7115,7315,"Do I make myself clear?"],[7394,7524,"No, but -"],[7524,7620,"Your Majesty -"],[7620,7770,"Yes."],[7770,7841,"Three hours it is."],[7841,7953,"I can get it done."],[8003,8124,"Harry!"],[8179,8299,"You be safe."]],"11":[[1527,1642,"Who's there?"],[5622,5747,"Drop the weapon."],[5747,5851,"Drop it!"],[6560,6669,"You owe me one, Your Highness."],[6690,6844,"Yeah all right."],[6844,6919,"Thanks."],[7465,7720,"I got a top quality shipment today."],[7720,8037,"It's yours if you name a good price."],[8124,8337,"There's a real gem in there, too."],[8337,8479,"It won't disappoint."],[8583,8700,"What do you want from me?"],[8700,8858,"Relax."],[8858,9004,"I'm just trying to give you a chance"],[9004,9096,"at a better life."],[9096,9313,"Believe me, once you get in those rich"],[9313,9563,"man's beds, you're actually gonna thank me."],[9563,9784,"I would stop right now if I were you."],[9784,9922,"You're going to make an enemy of the"],[9922,10014,"Royal family."],[10118,10301,"What are you, the Queen? Nonsense."],[10301,10443,"I'm not the Queen."],[10443,10694,"But I am the wife of the Prince,"],[10694,10890,"and the mother of the Royal heir."]],"12":[[87,271,"Hey! Don't move!"],[271,475,"Drop your weapons!"],[475,709,"I said drop your weapons or I'll kill her!"],[709,909,"Okay. All right."],[2927,3053,"Hey! You’re okay."],[3053,3115,"Come here."],[3115,3182,"You okay?"],[3182,3265,"Yeah."],[3265,3424,"I’m okay."],[3532,3645,"You okay?"],[3670,3920,"It's all over now, alright?"],[4012,4208,"All's well that ends well, huh Boss?"],[4208,4358,"Boss, you're quite the Romeo."],[4358,4496,"Still in love with Dr. Charlie"],[4496,4604,"after five years."],[4888,5038,"I heard you say that you were my wife."],[5038,5309,"I lied. I didn't want him to kill me."],[5330,5501,"And when you said that,"],[5501,5734,"your son was my heir, was that also a lie?"]],"13":[[308,671,"Hey Charlie! Hey! You okay?"],[1076,1242,"Charlie was shot. We need a Doctor!"],[1242,1384,"How did Dr. Charlie get shot?"],[1384,1497,"She needs surgery."],[1497,1647,"No, no. No need."],[1647,1889,"Daisy can take care of it. It's not a deep wound."],[1889,2035,"Your Highness, please put her on the bed."],[3136,3261,"You're useless."],[3261,3403,"You can't even take care of a girl."],[3403,3541,"What should we do next, ma'am?"],[3541,3841,"Well, for now, I want you to keep a low profile."],[4283,4446,"You are not getting away so easily"],[4446,4592,"next time, Charlie."],[4629,4838,"It's only an abrasion, Your Highness."],[4838,5084,"She'll be all right after a few days rest."],[5142,5305,"Your Highness, perhaps someone"],[5305,5480,"should take a look at you as well."],[5668,5872,"Ah no. I’m fine."],[5976,6156,"Can you give us a minute, please?"],[7169,7340,"I'm not the Queen,"],[7340,7582,"but I am the wife of a Prince"],[7582,7820,"and the mother of the Royal heir."]],"14":[[250,496,"Kyle."],[496,592,"Hey, I need you to look into"],[592,875,"Charlie and her child for me, all right?"],[925,1067,"Yeah, I need to know"],[1067,1330,"when he was born, and who the father is."],[1330,1564,"Thanks."],[1889,2135,"Who is the Father, Charlie?"],[2986,3144,"His Highness seems to be very worried"],[3144,3328,"about Dr. Charlie."],[3328,3528,"I wonder if he fancies her."],[3528,3699,"Dr. Charlie has a child."],[3699,3870,"He's probably just a good Prince."],[3870,4099,"I heard Charlie got shot because she jumped"],[4099,4295,"in front of a bullet that was coming for him"],[4295,4537,"so he’d feel indebted to her."],[4537,4688,"What a cunning bitch."],[4688,4767,"No!"],[4767,4913,"I feel like they know each other."],[4913,4954,"And -"],[4954,5042,"And what?"],[5088,5334,"The way he looks at her, it's not just -"],[5334,5463,"Charlie's a single mother."],[5463,5651,"You think His Highness would fancy her?"],[5651,5864,"I've known Dr. Charlie for years,"],[5864,6072,"and I've never met the child's father."],[6118,6477,"What if His Highness is the child's father?"],[6477,6635,"Oh, so that's why she jumped"],[6635,6790,"in front of the bullet for him!"],[6790,6956,"All's well that ends well."],[6956,7094,"Romantic, no?"],[7115,7399,"Oh please, he's a Prince."],[7399,7599,"I would jump in front of a bullet for him too."],[7820,7982,"Ladies!"],[7982,8229,"Did you come to the frontlines to gossip?"],[9934,10147,"Harry."]],"15":[[37,187,"Hi."],[266,421,"You are quite the hero,"],[421,721,"jumping in front of a bullet."],[871,1009,"How come you were out all day"],[1009,1159,"just from a little graze?"],[1188,1413,"You were here the whole time?"],[1472,1810,"Yeah, I- I fell asleep."],[2423,2656,"How could you fall asleep with that wound?"],[2790,3036,"Oh, uh."],[3274,3666,"Dr. Charlie, are you concerned as my doctor"],[3666,3966,"or as my ex-girlfriend?"],[3991,4241,"Hold on."],[5063,5130,"Sit back."],[5972,6272,"You know, it's my duty as a doctor."],[6385,6544,"Just doing my job."],[6806,6923,"Keep it dry."],[7457,7570,"You'll be fine."],[7570,7736,"You just need to keep it dry"],[7736,7899,"and disinfect it regularly."],[8441,8708,"Dr. Charlie,"],[8708,8979,"you are still as professional as ever."],[8979,9234,"Just like you were five years ago."],[9296,9363,"Do you remember?"],[9363,9505,"You told me those exact words."],[9980,10130,"Dr. Charlie."],[10130,10406,"Your nurses told me that you weren't hurt"],[10406,10602,"too bad, thankfully."],[10602,10885,"I am afraid that we are a bit short staffed today."],[10885,11131,"So if you could, please."],[11131,11411,"Yeah, absolutely. Yeah."],[11411,11599,"Excuse me."],[11782,11986,"Your Highness,"],[11986,12266,"I heard we got a special delivery of food"],[12266,12570,"from back home, if you would like to -"],[12570,12858,"I'm sorry, I can't today."]],"16":[[183,321,"Please help."],[321,621,"I can't stand this anymore."],[625,704,"Please."],[859,959,"Sir?"],[959,1088,"Doctor,"],[1088,1309,"may I have some more morphine."],[1309,1413,"It hurts."],[1413,1643,"It really hurts."],[1868,2047,"How did this happen?"],[2047,2143,"Who treated this?"],[2143,2402,"Dr. Charlie, there's not much we can do."],[2477,2677,"We're low on supplies."],[2677,2840,"He needs surgery, but -"],[2840,2944,"But what?"],[2944,3199,"The only surgeon available is Lady Selina."],[3199,3486,"But she's busy."],[3486,3645,"It's just a basic wound debridement."],[3645,4045,"All other doctors are sent to look after soldiers."],[4396,4717,"Lady Selina said he's just a local refugee."],[4717,4996,"Best not to bother."],[4996,5134,"Get the operating room ready."],[5134,5321,"What? Are you going to ask her to do it?"],[5321,5430,"No, I'll do it."],[5430,5663,"But you've just gotten hurt, are you sure?"],[5663,5830,"Just get the room ready."],[5830,5918,"If we’re low on supplies,"],[5918,6022,"you can put my name on it."],[6068,6289,"Right. Okay. Got it."],[6297,6535,"We're going to take care of you, okay?"],[6581,6690,"Let's go."],[7282,7382,"Dr. Charlie."],[7411,7615,"Remember to change the dressing."],[7653,7782,"Dr. Selina."],[7862,8062,"Is this how Dr. Charlie operates?"],[8062,8487,"With complete disregard to orders and hierarchy?"],[8491,8596,"I'm a doctor."],[8596,8762,"It's my duty to save lives."],[8762,9013,"Well, since you're so liberal about"],[9013,9334,"our limited supplies, as your supervisor,"],[9334,9517,"I'm in my full right to fire you."],[9517,9667,"Is there some kind of misunderstanding"],[9667,9751,"between us?"],[9801,10051,"You really think highly of yourself."],[10051,10151,"Don't you?"],[10151,10356,"Glad there's no misunderstanding, then."],[10414,10514,"Dr. Charlie."],[10681,10798,"Your mother."],[10798,11044,"She's, still receiving treatment"],[11044,11248,"at the same hospital, right?"],[11248,11344,"What do you want?"],[11344,11632,"Oh, nothing from you."],[11632,12041,"Just a friendly reminder to"],[12041,12345,"leave Harry alone."],[12345,12595,"I'm not vying after His Highness."],[12595,12783,"Good."]],"17":[[775,896,"Harry."],[946,1038,"You're a Prince."],[1038,1205,"I'm a civilian."],[1438,1772,"I actually came here to give you this."],[2002,2289,"So the cell signal is really bad around here."],[2289,2456,"And because Dr. Charlie"],[2456,2781,"has a habit of going into off limit areas,"],[2781,2982,"I thought it'd be a good idea for her to"],[2982,3232,"have a walkie-talkie with her next time."],[3415,3653,"I'll try not to get into more trouble."],[3716,3858,"Splendid."],[4779,4946,"Lady Selina?"],[4946,5117,"City Hospital called to say that half"],[5117,5280,"of our supply shipment have arrived"],[5280,5476,"and to send someone to go get it."],[5476,5747,"I checked the schedule."],[5747,5951,"I believe Dr. Charlie is done for the day."],[5951,6139,"Perhaps she can go get it?"],[6139,6335,"Brilliant."],[6335,6527,"If you wouldn't mind telling her."],[8099,8366,"You're not getting out of this one, Charlie."]],"18":[[809,1063,"A gorgeous girl like you and driving alone."],[1101,1372,"It can't be safe."],[1372,1455,"You want a ride?"],[1476,1710,"No thank you."],[2886,3040,"What's happening?"],[3082,3332,"Why isn’t it working?"],[5797,6085,"So the cell signal is really bad around here."],[6085,6268,"And because Dr. Charlie"],[6268,6548,"has a habit of going into off limit areas,"],[6577,6777,"I thought it'd be a good idea for her to"],[6777,7023,"have a walkie talkie with her next time."],[7686,8083,"Harry? It’s Charlie."],[8083,8233,"Can you hear me?"],[8375,8437,"Harry!"],[8437,8633,"It’s Charlie can you hear me?"],[8700,8933,"I drove into a minefield."],[8958,9167,"I’m gonna die here, Harry."]],"19":[[446,633,"Charlie?"],[817,967,"Fuck am I cursed?"],[967,1188,"I just got here, and I drove into a minefield!"],[1188,1380,"You have to take your finger off the button."],[1380,1568,"You can't hear me."],[2385,2569,"Why aren't you answering me?"],[2627,3069,"Stupid, stupid trash car."],[3069,3332,"If I get back, I'm gonna sue."],[3474,3774,"What's gonna happen to Nick?"],[3941,4175,"He’s so young."],[4175,4433,"What's he going to do without me?"],[4542,4938,"You know, if these are my last words, Harry."],[4938,5125,"I wanted to tell you that you haven't"],[5125,5401,"changed at all in the past five years."],[5401,5734,"You're still just as handsome and gentle"],[5734,5880,"and kind."],[5880,6064,"And I'm sorry for breaking up with you."],[6064,6222,"That was my bad."],[6222,6523,"But you know, you're not blameless."],[6523,6823,"You hid your true identity from me."],[6823,6881,"Because what?"],[6881,7228,"You thought that I was a gold digger?"],[7228,7741,"A social climber? Is that all you thought?"],[7741,7928,"You think so little of me."],[7928,8137,"No, that's not true, Charlie."],[8137,8266,"That's not true."],[8266,8383,"Hey, listen, I was try -"],[8383,8679,"You should know, Harry."],[8679,8888,"If I love somebody,"],[8888,9104,"it doesn't matter to me if they turn out"],[9104,9200,"to be homeless."],[9200,9351,"And if I hate somebody,"],[9351,9588,"it wouldn't matter even if they were the Prince."],[9617,9751,"Okay, but you are a Prince."],[9751,9939,"It doesn't matter to me."],[9939,10110,"That's what I'm saying, Harry."],[10110,10222,"Charlie."]],"20":[[0,304,"Charlie! Hey!"],[654,842,"You okay?"],[842,959,"What is wrong with you?"],[959,1101,"What about the landmines?"],[1142,1309,"You know what they call this?"],[1309,1568,"They call it a lover's suicide,"],[1568,1634,"if we step on it."],[1634,1835,"Just stop joking around, Harry."],[1835,2047,"It's not funny."],[2047,2202,"Come on, let's get you out of here."],[2202,2356,"No! What about the landmines?"],[2356,2464,"Come on. -I can walk."],[2464,2552,"Put me down!"],[2552,2752,"Okay, suit yourself. If you want to step on it."],[2752,2911,"No!"],[3319,3603,"You do love me after all."],[3603,3841,"Right, Charlie?"],[4579,4892,"Dr. Charlie,"],[4892,5084,"did you mean"],[5084,5384,"what you said on that walkie-talkie?"],[5518,5730,"You heard everything I said?"],[6823,7048,"Just don't lie to me."]],"21":[[37,112,"Your Highness!"],[112,204,"Are you all right?"],[204,425,"David?"],[2348,2569,"We were looking for you -"],[2631,2857,"We were looking for you for a while."],[2857,2948,"What happened to you?"],[2990,3090,"I want you to find out what happened"],[3090,3207,"to Charlie's car."],[3207,3336,"What?"],[3336,3465,"What happened to Charlie?"],[3490,3649,"Nothing happened to Charlie."],[3649,3795,"Find out what happened to the car."],[3841,3966,"Boss,"],[3966,4166,"it's obvious you care for her."],[4166,4300,"Why not just tell her?"],[4316,4642,"Because she has a child and a family,"],[4642,4909,"and she's happy."],[4909,5017,"I don’t want to get in the way of that."],[5017,5359,"But she's obviously into you."],[5359,5505,"And didn't you say her file"],[5505,5597,"said unmarried?"],[5597,5751,"So?"],[5751,5989,"Even if she's not married on paper,"],[5989,6131,"it doesn’t mean that she wasn’t with"],[6131,6360,"somebody back then, right?"],[6360,6427,"Who knows?"],[6427,6677,"But you love her."],[6677,6902,"Even if the kid's not yours, right?"],[7044,7244,"If you have half the nerve you had back then,"],[7244,7478,"I'm sure you can make it work."],[7490,7665,"Oh, yeah?"],[7665,7899,"Then what do you think I was trying to do outside?"]],"22":[[116,379,"Isn't that Harry's jacket?"],[379,679,"Was he riding in the same car as you?"],[679,838,"Is he all right?"],[838,1017,"What do you mean?"],[1017,1121,"How do you know something happened"],[1121,1267,"to the car?"],[1267,1505,"I didn't - I don't, I don't know what you mean."],[1505,1639,"It didn't happen by accident."],[1639,1830,"You did something to the car."],[1830,1968,"I have no idea what you're talking about."],[1968,2072,"I see you don't want to take credit"],[2072,2293,"for your brilliant plan, Lady Selina."],[2293,2531,"So what if I did it?"],[2531,2723,"I warned you."],[2723,3073,"I told you to stay away."],[3073,3282,"You wouldn't listen."],[3340,3557,"This is attempted murder, Selina."],[3582,3878,"Well, you're alive, aren't you?"],[3878,4045,"Where's your proof?"],[4045,4254,"Well,"],[4279,4517,"so what if I did it?"],[4517,4700,"I warned you."],[4700,4984,"I guess you still haven't learned your lesson."],[4984,5130,"What are you talking about?"],[5130,5255,"Are you dense?"],[5292,5655,"My father funded your hospital."],[5655,5960,"My family is the majority stakeholder."],[5960,6402,"So if you worry about your dear mother,"],[6402,6552,"I'd keep my mouth shut"],[6552,6690,"about what happened today."],[6690,6781,"No."],[6781,6994,"Selina, I'm gonna tell Harry."],[6994,7111,"Okay."],[7111,7444,"Well, it's not unusual for people to pass"],[7444,7678,"away at a hospital."],[7678,7937,"There’s no use in telling Harry."],[7937,8058,"Fine!"],[8128,8262,"I'll just make sure that nobody else"],[8262,8383,"finds out then."],[8383,8566,"Good girl."],[8566,8758,"And I will make sure that your mother"],[8758,9221,"is treated like a queen by our staff."],[9221,9801,"As long as you leave Harry alone."],[10143,10239,"Charlie!"]],"23":[[0,183,"Hey!"],[183,462,"I saw Selina, is she being mean to you again?"],[462,646,"No! Don't, Harry."],[646,779,"Stop it!"],[892,996,"Just leave it."],[1038,1263,"Charlie, if there is something bothering"],[1263,1526,"you, I want you to tell me, okay?"],[1526,1714,"I will help you."],[1810,2039,"No, nothing is bothering me."],[2039,2206,"I'm just going to go lie down."],[2206,2398,"Hey."],[2444,2786,"Is what you said on that walkie-talkie still true?"],[2823,2961,"Do you still love me?"],[3132,3294,"It was my fault"],[3294,3595,"to lie to you five years ago about who I was."],[3595,3741,"Okay, but I have thought about you"],[3741,3853,"every single day."],[3853,4145,"My love for you, is true."],[4162,4375,"I have never stopped thinking about you."],[4375,4821,"Charlie, will you please give me another chance?"],[4942,5080,"No, stop it!"],[5113,5159,"Okay."],[5159,5380,"It was over between us five years ago."],[5422,5597,"I only said all of that stuff because"],[5597,5751,"I thought I was dying."],[5751,5976,"Gavin and I have been together for the past"],[5976,6277,"five years, and we have a beautiful child together."],[6277,6544,"No, no."],[6544,6719,"You can't do that to me."],[6735,7002,"I'm sorry, Harry."],[7002,7190,"I’ve moved on."],[7857,8087,"I'm so sorry, Harry."]],"24":[[700,804,"Level 2 alert!"],[804,955,"We have a VIP patient dispatched"],[955,1146,"to the medical camp right now."],[1155,1263,"All right!"],[1263,1401,"All medics to their post immediately."],[1401,1505,"Let's go!"],[1739,1943,"This is the VIP patient's file,"],[1943,2097,"from his attending physician."],[2285,2389,"What is this?"],[2519,2652,"Everything's been redacted."],[2652,2798,"What are we supposed to look at?"],[2798,2982,"Well, the VIP cases we get are usually more"],[2982,3115,"fiction than fact."],[3144,3374,"So they're faking things in the file?"],[3374,3624,"These patients, their medical records"],[3624,3795,"are a vulnerability and a state secret."],[3958,4070,"The doctor can go in now."],[4462,4713,"The patient's blood pressure's very high."],[4713,4863,"His pulse is racing, and"],[4863,4984,"there are signs of drowsiness."],[4984,5125,"The file says the patient"],[5125,5246,"has a history of diabetes."],[5259,5472,"Maybe it's because of long term insulin use."],[5480,5618,"This is the medication prescribed"],[5618,5780,"by the attending physician."],[5889,6056,"This isn't something a diabetic patient"],[6056,6168,"should be using."],[6168,6331,"The high blood pressure isn’t caused"],[6331,6439,"by hypoglycemia."],[6439,6685,"It's low blood sugar from a heart condition."],[6685,6869,"The distended abdomen, the internal"],[6869,7027,"bleeding, the dropping blood pressure."],[7027,7215,"I mean, this patient has a lot going on."],[7215,7378,"We need to get him ready for surgery ASAP."],[7378,7494,"No!"],[7494,7607,"You can't perform surgery."],[7607,7778,"The attending will be here in an hour."],[7778,7887,"The patient doesn't have an hour."],[7887,8020,"We need to get him into surgery"],[8020,8137,"within the next 15 minutes."],[8137,8337,"We can't just have anyone operate."],[8337,8420,"I'm telling you,"],[8420,8558,"if we don't cut him open in the next"],[8558,8742,"15 minutes, this man is going to die."],[8742,8821,"Put your hands up!"]],"25":[[304,433,"Only doctors"],[433,604,"from the Emirates can operate"],[604,688,"on the Sheikh."],[721,1009,"Look, I'm not trying to change the rules here,"],[1009,1151,"but we really need to get this man"],[1151,1359,"in surgery right now if he’s going to live."],[1359,1539,"Blood pressure's dropping fast."],[1539,1676,"Charlie is just a doctor."],[1676,1985,"She's not qualified to make that call."],[1993,2102,"No."],[2102,2293,"You doctors can't even trust each other."],[2293,2439,"I'm not letting any of you operate."],[2439,2498,"That’s it."],[2498,2631,"We have ten minutes to get"],[2631,2744,"this guy out of here."],[2744,2819,"Your Highness,"],[2819,3032,"this isn't just a matter of life and death."],[3032,3257,"This is about who is responsible."],[3257,3390,"If something goes wrong"],[3390,3591,"and it's the fault of one of our doctors,"],[3591,3874,"it's going to be a diplomatic disaster."],[3874,4129,"We can't act recklessly."],[4129,4429,"You represent the Royal family."],[4554,4884,"If something goes wrong, it's -"],[4884,5267,"the consequences are gonna be, unthinkable."],[5451,5559,"Can you save him?"],[5584,5747,"We need to open him up to know for sure,"],[5747,5839,"but I think there's -"],[5839,6118,"Just answer my question."],[6177,6318,"Can you save him?"],[6352,6740,"Charlie, if you blunder, it's not just on you."],[6740,7023,"It's on our nation."],[7023,7082,"You -"],[7082,7211,"I will take full responsibility"],[7211,7353,"for what happens next."]],"26":[[25,379,"Harry, the King will not approve."],[617,850,"Harry, what the hell are you doing?"],[850,1084,"This isn't the time to be reckless."],[1084,1222,"If you fail, it could lead to"],[1222,1484,"Diplomatic disaster, or worse"],[1484,1655,"could start a war."],[1655,1735,"Have you even thought about"],[1735,1830,"the consequences?"],[1830,2031,"That's exactly why I'm doing this."],[2056,2310,"Dr. Charlie,"],[2310,2523,"I'm going to need you to answer one thing."],[2544,2686,"Can you save him?"],[3078,3340,"Yes, I can save him."],[3782,3983,"Then get the surgery ready right now."],[4104,4195,"Harry."],[4195,4450,"Are you out of your mind?"],[4450,4708,"David, from now on, you have permission"],[4708,4775,"to shoot anyone"],[4775,4996,"who attempts to interrupt the surgery."],[5246,5367,"What are you doing?"],[5367,5597,"You focus on your job."],[5597,5822,"The doctor's going to save the patient."],[5822,5943,"And I'm going to protect"],[5943,6056,"whoever I need to protect."]],"27":[[116,308,"Are we really doing this?"],[308,500,"This surgery is too risky."],[500,754,"Not just for the patient, but for us"],[754,942,"and the soldiers outside."],[975,1163,"If we don't act now, this patient will die."],[1301,1501,"As doctors, we don't have the luxury of choosing"],[1501,1668,"when to step back."],[2360,2469,"Scalpel."],[5238,5401,"Surgery was a success."],[6356,6439,"You did great."],[6439,6652,"What if I had told you I'd failed?"],[6669,6765,"Probably would have put you on"],[6765,6856,"the first plane out."],[7007,7148,"And what about you?"],[7148,7244,"You're not planning on"],[7244,7403,"running away with me?"],[7453,7661,"Oh wait, I forgot you’re a Prince."],[7866,8128,"I would go anywhere with you."],[8128,8220,"And you know what?"],[8220,8462,"I will always be there"],[8462,8612,"protecting you."],[8641,8796,"Okay, enough jokes for today,"],[8796,8942,"Your Highness."],[9409,9572,"I wasn't joking."],[10739,10835,"Excuse me."],[10944,11094,"I'm Dr. Caesar, the Sheikh’s"],[11094,11286,"attending physician."],[11286,11403,"I've come to thank the surgeon"],[11403,11619,"who operated on His Majesty."],[11657,11878,"He'd like to give this gift."],[11932,12208,"This will give you access to everything"],[12208,12420,"your heart desires in the Emirates."],[12470,12529,"Now,"],[12529,12754,"which kind hearted doctor do I have the"],[12754,12892,"pleasure of thanking?"],[12892,12946,"It's -"],[12946,13075,"It's me."]],"28":[[412,500,"It's me."],[500,658,"Selina, what the hell are"],[658,767,"you talking about?"],[767,855,"The one who risked -"],[855,1026,"Be quiet."],[1092,1343,"So, who was it?"],[1343,1472,"It was me, Sir."],[1472,1755,"No, it was her Dr. Charlie."],[1856,2064,"Think of your mother."],[2064,2252,"Well, why don't we let"],[2252,2464,"Dr. Charlie speak for herself?"],[2464,2673,"Charlie, just tell them it was you."],[2907,3098,"It was Dr. Selina."],[3132,3282,"She was the one who prepared"],[3282,3353,"the surgery plan"],[3353,3470,"and she's the one who"],[3470,3557,"performed the surgery."],[3557,3728,"She saved his life."],[3728,4024,"You are very kind and wonderful."],[4024,4124,"Thank you."],[4124,4379,"I thank you for saving his life."],[4379,4458,"Wait."],[4521,4633,"You know, I think there's been a little"],[4633,4800,"misunderstanding here."],[4879,5146,"She is not the doctor"],[5146,5413,"who saved the Sheikh's life."],[5563,5864,"The doctor who saved the Sheikh's life"],[5968,6177,"was Dr. Charlie."]],"29":[[20,129,"It was you."],[271,596,"You are very kind hearted and wonderful"],[596,896,"and beautiful, inside and out."],[963,1305,"On behalf of His Majesty, I thank you."],[1305,1463,"Oh, it's really not necessary."],[1463,1564,"I was just doing my job."],[1564,1772,"I insist."],[1772,1951,"It's just a small token of gratitude"],[1951,2043,"from our Sheikh."],[2177,2281,"Thank you."],[2281,2515,"I appreciate it."],[3591,3703,"Father."],[3703,3853,"Do something."],[3853,4124,"That bitch Charlie, she's going to steal"],[4124,4195,"Harry."],[4195,4308,"I've heard about everything"],[4308,4391,"going on over there."],[4391,4479,"Don't worry."],[4479,4717,"I'll contact the hospital, get her removed"],[4717,4892,"from the team, and revoke her license."],[4892,5088,"She'll be out of Harry's sight for good."],[5088,5246,"Brilliant."],[5246,5513,"But what if Harry interferes?"],[5513,5593,"Don't worry."],[5593,5893,"The King won't allow it."],[6214,6360,"Dr. Charlie."],[6360,6523,"The hospital just issued a statement."],[6535,6760,"They've revoked your medical license"],[6760,6994,"and certification."],[7052,7182,"And you've been fired."],[7261,7415,"How is that possible?"],[7415,7570,"It's gotta be Selina."],[7570,7720,"She tried to take your credit,"],[7720,7836,"and when that didn't work,"],[7836,8074,"she's gone behind your back with this."],[8162,8299,"My mom's still in the hospital."],[8299,8525,"I can't lose my job and my license."],[9488,9743,"While this matter has been resolved for now,"],[9763,10022,"we need to determine who is responsible"],[10022,10160,"for this major accident."],[10160,10356,"Yes, Your Majesty, I take"],[10356,10589,"full responsibility for what happened."],[10785,10994,"I hear there was also a female doctor"],[10994,11261,"involved, who's been fired."],[11261,11323,"Yes."],[11323,11724,"I was actually just about to address that situation."],[11724,11995,"Dr. Charlie's exceptional skills"],[11995,12187,"were pivotal on this case,"],[12187,12458,"and I wanted to ask,"],[12458,12575,"I do hope you write a"],[12575,12821,"formal commendation letter in her name"],[12821,12971,"on behalf of the royal family,"],[12971,13263,"recognizing the outstanding contributions"],[13263,13434,"that she has made to the medical project."],[13434,13651,"This way the hospital won't be able"],[13651,13888,"to dismiss her so easily."],[13888,14189,"Harry, that was Duke Ford's decision."],[14222,14435,"Now you know what he wants."],[14435,14752,"I'll issue a commendation to Dr. Charlie,"],[14752,14914,"but in exchange,"],[14914,15256,"you will return to the country immediately"],[15256,15536,"and marry the Duke's daughter, Selina."],[15536,15836,"Yes, I agree."]],"30":[[262,500,"Mommy, I miss you so much."],[500,738,"Oh, I miss you too, Nicky."],[738,1205,"So, mommy, have you found dad yet?"],[1317,1568,"So, you still haven't told Harry?"],[1580,1839,"Gavin, he's getting married."],[1839,2039,"Exactly why you should tell him."],[2160,2477,"He's a Prince, Gavin."],[2477,2610,"He shouldn't have to be married"],[2610,2719,"to someone like me."],[2719,2869,"Yeah, but he is Nick's father."],[2944,3157,"Mommy, I miss dad."],[3199,3386,"I miss him, too, Nick."],[3386,3574,"Go talk to him."],[3574,3816,"Whatever he decides is his decision,"],[3816,4016,"but he should know."],[4166,4241,"Mom,"],[4241,4579,"can you and dad please come home together?"],[4617,4967,"Yeah, I promise I will."],[5843,5943,"Dr. Charlie."],[6001,6156,"Are you looking for His Highness?"],[6293,6544,"He left early this morning."],[6544,6685,"He didn't tell you?"],[6785,6911,"Harry."],[6911,7127,"You couldn't even say goodbye."]],"31":[[29,179,"Daisy."],[200,304,"Is there any way that we can"],[304,400,"catch up with him?"],[421,688,"He left two hours ago."],[688,1001,"I mean, we could try, but even if we drive,"],[1001,1121,"we won't make it."],[3090,3265,"Dr. Charlie,"],[3265,3374,"you saved my life."],[3420,3782,"My promise can bring you wealth or power"],[3782,3903,"beyond what most people"],[3903,4041,"can ever dream of."],[4087,4270,"Are you sure you just want to use it"],[4270,4441,"to catch a helicopter ride?"],[4446,4583,"I’m sure."],[4583,4733,"This is worth more to me than any"],[4733,4813,"amount of money."],[4929,5050,"May I ask why?"],[5063,5280,"Because"],[5280,5480,"I need to tell someone the truth."],[5480,5743,"That I've always loved him."],[5743,5905,"It's never changed."],[5905,6039,"My son and I,"],[6039,6202,"we've thought about him every single day"],[6202,6360,"for the last five years."],[6381,6552,"I understand."],[6606,6781,"He must be someone important in your life."],[6940,7044,"Will you help me?"],[7803,7912,"Of course."],[7912,8024,"You're my savior!"],[8083,8366,"I wish you all the best in finding your happiness."],[8546,8712,"You didn't tell Dr. Charlie when you left"],[8712,8913,"so, what are you expecting now?"],[8913,9071,"Who said that I was waiting for her?"],[9071,9230,"Come on."],[9230,9380,"Stop lying to yourself, Your Highness."],[9467,9672,"Why not tell Charlie that you're marrying"],[9672,9830,"Selina for her sake?"],[9830,9959,"Because I don't want her to think that"],[9959,10143,"she's the one that's holding me back."],[10143,10260,"I want her to know that"],[10260,10397,"everything that I'm doing,"],[10397,10598,"I’m doing for her willingly."],[10873,11023,"It’s time to board, Your Highness."],[12312,12483,"Harry!"],[13642,13767,"Harry."],[13767,13918,"I need to talk to you."]],"32":[[62,183,"I need to talk to you."],[316,437,"Nick is actually -"],[437,742,"Oh well, if it isn't Dr. Charlie."],[784,1180,"Are you here to see off His Highness too?"],[1284,1501,"Yes. I came to see him off."],[1814,1856,"Okay."],[1856,2118,"Well, now that we've said our goodbyes,"],[2118,2406,"Your Highness, you should get going."],[2406,2515,"You don't want to be late."],[2560,2802,"Charlie, what were you going to say?"],[2831,3111,"Nick is who?"],[3294,3812,"If you are worried about your dear mother,"],[3812,3949,"I'd keep my mouth shut"],[3949,4112,"about what happened today."],[4116,4216,"No."],[4216,4441,"Selina, I’m gonna tell Harry."],[4441,4554,"Okay."],[4554,4892,"Well, it's not unusual for people to pass away"],[4892,5067,"at a hospital."],[5117,5351,"There's no use in telling Harry."],[5438,5576,"Sorry, Harry."],[5576,5701,"I can't say it."],[5701,5893,"Nothing."],[5893,6177,"You must have misheard me, Sir."],[6243,6464,"Charlie."],[6464,6648,"Trust me."],[6648,6827,"I have missed you so much for the past"],[6827,6881,"five years."],[6881,7077,"I need you to tell me exactly right now,"],[7077,7211,"what were you going to say?"],[7920,8153,"Your Highness."],[8153,8262,"Things have changed over the"],[8262,8387,"past five years."],[8387,8700,"I'm with somebody else, and I have a child."],[8721,8925,"So you came all this way,"],[9021,9154,"just to say that?"],[9597,9659,"I came to tell you"],[9659,9959,"that it's not going to work."],[9976,10276,"And congratulations on your engagement."],[11177,11282,"Harry."],[11282,11557,"What I really wanted to say is,"],[11557,11765,"I love you."]],"33":[[467,684,"Haven't we settled our business?"],[684,825,"Relax, Lady Selina."],[867,1172,"I just need you to do us one more small favor."],[1172,1322,"Don't be foolish."],[1322,1564,"You couldn't even get rid of Charlie last time."],[1564,1843,"I don't need your services anymore."],[1843,1906,"Oh, yeah?"],[1906,2089,"Well, I guess you won't mind if"],[2089,2369,"Prince Harry finds out about all this, will you?"],[2410,2510,"What do you want?"],[2510,2769,"Just take in one more patient."],[2890,3032,"Fine."],[3032,3332,"But this is the last time."],[3349,3649,"Don't ever contact me again."],[4245,4354,"Selina?"],[4391,4529,"This is a war zone."],[4529,4758,"We need to test our patients for viruses"],[4758,4892,"before treating them."],[4892,5196,"Are you really going to let this woman die?"],[5196,5380,"This isn't like you, Dr. Charlie."],[5451,5580,"Where did this patient come from?"],[5672,5960,"I am your supervisor."],[5960,6126,"Just get the room ready."],[6277,6452,"Daisy."],[6452,6656,"Can you take a sample?"],[6656,6806,"Run the tests."],[7461,7645,"Why does it look like she's infected?"],[7686,7786,"Dr. Charlie, something’s wrong!"],[7786,7932,"The patient’s vomiting blood,"],[7932,8074,"possibly some internal bleeding."],[8074,8141,"What?"]],"34":[[542,738,"What are you waiting for?"],[738,967,"Dr. Selina, I believe this patient is infected"],[967,1159,"with a mystery virus."],[1159,1305,"If we don't wait for the test results"],[1305,1484,"to come back, and we just go and operate,"],[1484,1626,"all of our colleagues lives"],[1626,1839,"are going to be put at risk."],[1839,2160,"Are you insinuating that I have brought"],[2160,2460,"a mystery virus to our camp?"],[2569,2761,"It's your name on the records,"],[2761,2857,"Dr. Charlie."],[2877,3065,"I'm not trying to pass the blame,"],[3065,3278,"but I think we need to wait."],[3820,3870,"Yeah."],[3870,3953,"Hello there."],[3958,4229,"The patient you sent me couldn't possibly be"],[4229,4504,"infected with some kind of virus."],[4504,4608,"How’d you know?"],[4675,4838,"Are you serious?"],[4838,4979,"I can't treat her."],[4979,5138,"She is infected with the newest virus"],[5138,5305,"developed in our labs,"],[5305,5492,"and the only living carrier."],[5492,5743,"If she dies, I'll expose everything"],[5743,5880,"you've ever done, online."],[5880,6131,"So if I were you, Lady Selina,"],[6131,6677,"I would do my very best to save her life."],[7503,7699,"Start the surgery now."],[7699,7841,"That's an order."],[8195,8279,"Stop!"],[8279,8404,"We have the test results."],[8404,8550,"The patient tested positive for the"],[8550,8675,"deadly M virus!"],[8883,9029,"Dr. Charlie!"]],"35":[[579,721,"Quarantine this area immediately."],[771,905,"Notify the command center."],[905,1080,"We need everybody in this medical facility"],[1080,1317,"tested for the virus."],[1718,1776,"No matter what,"],[1776,1951,"I'm going to save this patient's life."],[1960,2189,"We're not stopping the surgery."],[3820,3958,"Dr. Charlie,"],[3958,4187,"you've tested positive for the M virus."],[4233,4404,"We've notified the command center."],[4404,4654,"Antibodies will be sent shortly but,"],[4654,4750,"it'll take a few days"],[4750,5113,"to develop a vaccine combining the pathogen."],[5113,5326,"You have to hang on."],[5326,5543,"Send in some medical supplies."],[5543,5709,"I'll handle the post-op care."],[6026,6114,"David."],[6327,6443,"Can you get me the walkie talkie"],[6443,6531,"that Harry sent me?"],[6531,6819,"Don't worry Dr. Charlie."],[6819,6902,"You'll be fine."],[6952,7077,"I’ll notify His Highness and I’ll bring"],[7077,7157,"the medical team in."],[7157,7444,"No, you cannot tell Harry about this."],[7599,7799,"It's too dangerous."],[7974,8174,"Understood."],[8174,8475,"Harry."],[8475,8929,"I miss you so much."]],"36":[[229,475,"Your wedding to Lady Selina"],[475,638,"has been arranged"],[638,804,"for the third week after her return."],[804,1009,"All right, well, you know what?"],[1009,1130,"You can take care of it."],[1176,1334,"But His Majesty has"],[1334,1463,"made all these arrangements for you."],[1463,1605,"My father wants me to get married"],[1605,1755,"for his sake and for the country."],[1755,1943,"Other than that, he doesn’t care."],[1943,2081,"Oh, you know what?"],[2118,2252,"How’s that matter that I asked you"],[2252,2356,"to look into while I was in Troy?"],[2419,2652,"Well Your Highness, I did look into it"],[2652,2752,"and"],[2752,2898,"it seems Dr. Charlie's mother"],[2898,3082,"is in critically ill condition."],[3103,3307,"She's at Ford hospital."],[3307,3420,"She's been there for five years,"],[3420,3528,"and she's awaiting a heart transplant."],[3591,3828,"And Dr. Charlie,"],[3828,3999,"has been fronting the entire bill."],[4091,4225,"Listen, I don’t want to be too blunt but as a"],[4225,4287,"resident doctor"],[4287,4429,"that's a lot to take on."],[4429,4637,"She has a substantial,"],[4637,4796,"substantial amount of debt."],[4821,5100,"Ford hospital?"],[5100,5255,"Why does that name sound so familiar?"],[5255,5388,"Is that -"],[5388,5559,"is that under Selina’s Father?"],[5559,5659,"Yes."],[5659,5922,"It is Duke Ford’s hospital."],[6339,6481,"Hey!"],[6481,6723,"I saw Selina, is she being mean to you again?"],[6723,6765,"Because -"],[6765,6948,"No, don’t Harry!"],[6948,7082,"Stop it!"],[7194,7298,"Just leave it."],[7323,7603,"Has Selina been threatening Charlie?"],[7603,7724,"And as for the birth record"],[7724,7878,"of Dr. Charlie's son."],[7916,8070,"We found it, it’s from five years ago."],[8070,8370,"But there's no indication of a father."],[8566,8754,"And she has never been married."],[8837,9121,"Charlie, what are you hiding from me, huh?"]],"37":[[25,145,"Gavin!"],[383,567,"You tell me something."],[567,684,"Why didn't you marry Charlie?"],[684,792,"Harry?"],[850,963,"What are you talking about?"],[963,1084,"Well, let me ask you a question."],[1084,1247,"Was it because of her mother, right?"],[1247,1313,"Exactly."],[1313,1480,"You finally understand."],[1480,1714,"I mean, five years ago, Charlie just wanted to -"],[1714,1810,"How could you do that?"],[1810,1922,"You knew that her mother was sick"],[1922,2043,"and didn't want to be a burden to her?"],[2043,2102,"Is that what it is?"],[2102,2218,"What are you talking about?"],[2218,2364,"You were the one who abandoned her"],[2364,2448,"five years ago."],[2448,2510,"Me?"],[2523,2702,"I left because you were having"],[2702,2798,"an affair with her!"],[2798,2911,"That's because you were lying"],[2911,3094,"about your identity the whole time."],[3094,3207,"Why? Because,"],[3207,3307,"Because she can't love me if I was"],[3307,3449,"an ordinary soldier."],[3449,3549,"But she can only love me"],[3549,3703,"because I'm a Prince, right?"],[3712,3991,"You know what? I can't even."],[3991,4133,"You're not even hearing anything"],[4133,4187,"I'm saying."],[4187,4404,"Right there. I got you."],[4404,4542,"Because you're guilty."],[4542,4688,"If I had known that you were an"],[4688,4842,"absolute piece of trash,"],[5013,5201,"I would have never let you have her"],[5201,5376,"in the first place."],[5405,5668,"Stop arguing."],[5718,5847,"It's okay, Nick."],[5847,6043,"You don't need to cry, alright?"],[6043,6202,"You know what, Nick? I’m sorry, okay?"],[6202,6477,"I didn't mean to talk like that."],[6506,6644,"Daddy!"]],"38":[[112,337,"Who are you calling daddy, huh?"],[337,462,"You're daddy!"],[462,617,"Mommy, showed me your photo."],[688,1076,"This kid, he is confused, right?"],[1184,1272,"Aren't you his dad?"],[1359,1455,"How is he confused"],[1455,1572,"If you're standing right here?"],[1589,1768,"That's none of your business."],[1768,2010,"I mean, it's not like this is your kid anyway."],[2064,2256,"You tell me right now."],[2256,2560,"Whose kid is this actually?"],[2827,2986,"Hey, Nick."],[3219,3653,"Did your mommy tell you I was your daddy?"],[3958,4049,"Your Highness!"],[4049,4154,"Bad news from Troy."],[4245,4396,"There’s been an outbreak of the M virus"],[4396,4533,"created by the terrorist group."],[4637,4758,"Charlie."],[4758,4817,"All right, you know what?"],[4817,5005,"Kyle, I'm gonna need a private jet."],[5005,5155,"I need to get to Troy as soon as possible."],[5155,5292,"But, Your Highness, you can't -"],[5292,5492,"That is an order."],[5559,5684,"Yes, sir."],[6014,6181,"Gosh, Charlie."],[6181,6293,"Uncle Gavin."],[6393,6581,"What's happening with mommy?"],[6581,6715,"Hey."],[6715,7015,"Don't worry, okay?"],[7015,7253,"Daddy’s going to bring mommy home soon."],[7253,7528,"I promise."],[7928,8049,"Father."],[8049,8237,"Why will you not let me go to Troy?"],[8237,8475,"Harry, you are a Prince."],[8558,8721,"The most important thing right now"],[8721,8858,"is preparing for your wedding."],[8954,9188,"And I've already sent a support team to Troy."],[9188,9526,"Oh, come on. That's nonsense."],[9526,9663,"I am also a soldier."],[9864,10155,"And first and foremost. You are Royalty."],[10155,10381,"The mother of my son is there right now"],[10381,10527,"and I'm not going to just sit around"],[10527,10631,"while she's in danger."],[10631,10835,"What did you just say?"],[10910,11011,"You have a son?"],[11011,11148,"Yes."],[11148,11357,"And his mother is Dr. Charlie"],[11357,11473,"and she's there right now,"],[11473,11649,"in the outbreak zone."]],"39":[[688,817,"Father,"],[817,946,"I’m sorry that I lied to you,"],[946,1238,"but Charlie means too much to me."],[1238,1526,"I can't lose her."],[2861,3132,"Calling Harry."],[3132,3307,"Calling Harry."],[3436,3741,"How are you feeling?"],[3741,4041,"Have you eaten anything today?"],[4099,4483,"God, Harry, I miss you so much."],[4617,5063,"And I might die here."],[5096,5267,"Nick, I'm so sorry."],[5292,5551,"Harry, I should have told you the truth"],[5551,5663,"from the beginning."],[5663,5851,"But I never betrayed you."],[5851,6135,"Nick is your son."],[6135,6348,"You have no idea how badly"],[6348,6610,"I wish the three of us could be a family."],[6719,7040,"Harry, I love you,"],[7040,7307,"and I have always loved you."],[7407,7536,"Can you hear me?"],[7691,7811,"Yes."],[7895,8083,"I can hear you."],[8216,8379,"And I love you too."]],"40":[[592,792,"You need to get out of here"],[792,975,"before you get infected too."],[975,1138,"But I'm already infected."],[1180,1259,"What?"],[1818,2085,"Harry! Were you worried about me?"],[2085,2344,"I'm fine. I wasn't infected."],[2423,2489,"Where's Charlie?"],[2489,2652,"In the isolation zone."],[2694,2886,"It's always about Charlie."],[2886,3019,"Why her?"],[3019,3186,"Wait, so the antibody has not been"],[3186,3249,"developed yet?"],[3249,3428,"We're working on the tests, but right now,"],[3428,3649,"there are too few infected cases."],[3661,3832,"We don't have enough test subjects,"],[3832,3966,"so we're looking for volunteers."],[3966,4149,"The virus progresses quickly."],[4149,4341,"We're afraid we won't have enough time."],[4341,4550,"Wait, so, if you guys had one more infected"],[4550,4650,"case, then"],[4650,4800,"the antibody could be developed?"],[4800,4975,"In theory, yes."],[5000,5117,"I'll do it."],[5384,5555,"Do you have any idea how dangerous"],[5555,5684,"this virus is?"],[5780,5885,"I missed you."],[5885,6239,"But you could die. We can't risk that."],[6389,6506,"But I missed you."],[6748,7019,"Now I understand what you're saying."],[7019,7194,"But I can't stand to not be with you"],[7194,7340,"any longer."]],"41":[[375,525,"Have you eaten anything yet?"],[571,679,"I miss you."],[821,967,"Are you feeling all right?"],[1030,1142,"I miss you."],[1197,1326,"I miss you too."],[2077,2189,"The vaccine is ready."],[2189,2277,"Be careful."],[2277,2569,"This is all we can make for now."],[2569,2873,"I will help administer these."],[3199,3315,"The vaccine’s ready?"],[3315,3353,"Yeah."],[3353,3520,"Unfortunately, they were only able"],[3520,3653,"to make one dose."],[3724,3862,"Who should I save?"],[3862,3974,"What are you talking about?"],[3974,4074,"There's two doses."],[4358,4508,"Oopsy."],[4508,4838,"Like I said, there's only one dose."],[4884,5071,"So Charlie,"],[5071,5259,"who do you think I should save?"],[5601,5734,"I can't believe this happened."],[5734,5814,"What are we going to do?"],[5814,6068,"These things happen, that’s the life of a doctor."],[6068,6177,"Where's Charlie?"],[6177,6277,"She wasn’t with me when we"],[6277,6381,"finished the injection."],[6381,6602,"Harry."],[6602,6706,"It's all my fault."],[6727,6881,"I accidentally dropped"],[6881,7069,"one of the vaccine bottles."],[7069,7253,"Dr. Charlie has sacrificed"],[7253,7344,"her own dose for you."],[7344,7457,"What?"]],"42":[[37,225,"So you're saying there's no other"],[225,337,"option to get another dose?"],[337,479,"We're out of supplies."],[479,617,"Even if we get the next shipment,"],[617,704,"it'll be too late."],[704,850,"There's no other option?"],[905,1167,"No. It's too bad."],[1167,1480,"But I never expected Dr. Charlie"],[1480,1693,"to be so selfless."],[1705,1943,"I'm truly grateful for her sacrifice."],[1993,2110,"Charlie."],[2110,2293,"No! There is another way."],[2293,2581,"This virus was created by a terrorist group."],[2581,2877,"They must have the virus sample in serum,"],[2877,3048,"or they’ll get infected too."],[3048,3190,"David."],[3265,3399,"I want you to get the location of the"],[3399,3661,"terrorist group in 15, and get the gear."],[3661,3732,"We leave in 20."],[3732,3820,"Yes, Your Highness."],[3820,3941,"No, Harry. No!"],[3941,4108,"You are royalty."],[4108,4446,"You can't risk your life just for her."],[4446,4592,"And who are you to tell me what I can"],[4592,4763,"or can't do, huh?"],[4763,4875,"She is the one that I love."],[4875,5134,"But I am your fiancée!"],[5134,5242,"Not anymore."],[5384,5488,"I'm marrying Charlie."],[5488,5672,"She already has a child."],[5672,5822,"I don’t mind."],[6460,6581,"Your Highness, we've temporarily"],[6581,6735,"slowed down the virus activity"],[6735,6840,"with cooling."],[7494,7766,"Charlie, I want you to wait for me."],[7791,7924,"I'm going to come back,"],[7924,8049,"and I'm going to save you."],[8049,8387,"Please don't risk your life for me, Harry."],[8387,8550,"Promise me that you'll be safe."],[8896,8996,"I promise."]],"43":[[2698,2902,"Harry I’m so cold."],[4083,4200,"Your Highness, are you okay?"],[4200,4404,"No I’m fine! Okay?"],[4404,4608,"We gotta keep going."],[4775,5146,"It was so good to see you again, Harry."],[5313,5426,"Having been loved by"],[5426,5793,"you is one of the best parts of my life."],[7361,7582,"I'm coming for you, Charlie."],[8003,8233,"Harry."],[8233,8604,"I don't think I'm gonna make it."]],"44":[[196,329,"Hey!"],[350,492,"Harry!"],[492,696,"Charlie."],[696,880,"I was so afraid of losing you."],[892,1192,"I'm okay now."],[1305,1459,"You're hurt."],[1584,1993,"Oh. Yeah."],[2089,2331,"I guess I'm going to have to"],[2331,2519,"call my doctor again, huh?"],[2519,2736,"Is His Highness afraid of having women"],[2736,2932,"he doesn't know, see him naked?"],[2932,3086,"Yeah."],[3086,3265,"That's why I only have one trusted"],[3265,3566,"Doctor and one love of my life."],[3745,3870,"Charlie."],[3870,4166,"For the last five years,"],[4212,4446,"I have never stopped loving you."],[6715,7011,"You left me no choice, Charlie."],[7966,8137,"Something isn't right, Charlie."],[8179,8270,"What's going on?"],[8270,8379,"Is it Nick?"],[8379,8462,"No."],[8462,8641,"It's your mom."],[8641,8800,"The hospital called me today to tell me"],[8800,8950,"they're terminating her treatments"],[8950,9109,"because of late payment."],[9109,9205,"What?"],[9205,9388,"Look, I asked my friend to help your mom"],[9388,9567,"for now, but you have to do something."],[10206,10410,"How dare you, Selina!"],[10452,10635,"I warned you."],[10656,11077,"I told you to stay away from Harry."],[11077,11257,"What you did was illegal."],[11257,11361,"You know that, right?"],[11361,11448,"Yeah."],[11448,11599,"And who’s gonna believe you?"],[11599,11845,"My father is the Duke of Ford,"],[11845,12099,"in case you've forgotten already."],[12099,12516,"So, for the last time, leave Harry alone,"],[12516,12725,"or you might not make it out alive."],[12758,12875,"So you're really doing this?"],[12892,13004,"Are you scared?"],[13054,13213,"No."],[13213,13371,"But you should be."],[13371,13601,"Selina!"]],"45":[[62,354,"I didn't know that you could stoop so low."],[354,558,"You know, I've already talked to the Duke."],[558,684,"You'll be heading home immediately."],[684,825,"Harry, you've got to believe me."],[825,1013,"Charlie, she set me up!"],[1013,1151,"Oh give me a break!"],[1151,1292,"I heard your entire conversation."],[1292,1518,"Not just me, but the entire camp."],[1518,1693,"I am your fiancée."],[1693,1818,"Not anymore."],[1856,2014,"Your family has already been notified"],[2014,2206,"by the King's office."],[2206,2310,"You’ll hear soon enough."],[2310,2460,"This is all because of you."],[2460,2565,"You bitch!"],[2565,2660,"David!"],[2711,2806,"Take her away."],[2806,2923,"No, no no no no no!"],[2923,3053,"Don't touch me!"],[3053,3178,"Do not touch me!"],[3178,3461,"Do not, do not, I am gonna -"],[3461,3724,"I am gonna cut your funding. I am gonna -"],[3724,4012,"Put me down. Put me down!"],[4333,4441,"Dr. Charlie."],[4487,4650,"I've arranged for your mother"],[4650,4863,"to be sent to a new hospital."],[4963,5138,"And we found a perfect fit for her"],[5138,5447,"heart transplant, so,"],[5476,5576,"so she's going to be scheduled"],[5576,5697,"for surgery very soon."],[5726,5893,"Really?"],[5893,5985,"Thank you."],[6010,6310,"Well, you know, it's the least I can do for you."],[6418,6573,"Do you remember the first time we met?"],[6598,6790,"Yeah. You were wounded."],[6790,6936,"I treated you,"],[6936,7052,"and I thought you were in a gang."],[7052,7228,"Yes."],[7307,7674,"So, when do you think Dr. Charlie's"],[7674,7857,"going to fulfill her promises?"],[7857,8049,"What promises?"],[8049,8166,"I don't know."],[8166,8245,"Treat me."],[8245,8495,"Examine me."],[8495,8625,"Dr. Charlie said that she would"],[8625,8733,"take care of me."],[9588,9755,"Harry."],[9755,9914,"Thank you so much for everything you've"],[9914,10039,"done for me."]],"46":[[367,475,"Haven’t we settled everything?"],[492,613,"Thanks to you, lady,"],[613,767,"my whole base has been wiped out"],[767,846,"by Prince Harry."],[871,1026,"I'm on the most wanted list,"],[1026,1347,"so no, things are definitely not settled."],[1351,1488,"Are you serious?"],[1488,1735,"If it wasn't for your ineptitude then,"],[1735,1868,"Charlie would have been killed"],[1868,2072,"and none of this would have happened."],[2698,2886,"You really want to kill that woman?"],[2927,3115,"How about this?"],[3115,3378,"You help me get rid of her,"],[3570,3787,"and I will help you get out of the country."],[3945,4108,"Deal."],[5096,5326,"Mommy, when are you coming home?"],[5326,5601,"Soon, Nicky. Very soon."],[5601,5818,"So you're coming home with daddy?"],[5960,6064,"Charlie."],[6064,6268,"Don't tell me you still haven't told Harry."],[6581,6777,"I don't know how, okay?"],[6777,6890,"I don't know what to say."],[6936,7173,"Come on, you are overthinking this."],[7173,7298,"Haven't you two gotten back"],[7298,7424,"together already?"],[7424,7640,"Why not just talk with him about what happened?"],[7665,7920,"All right, I'll tell Harry."],[7920,8066,"So, Mommy,"],[8066,8212,"you're coming back with daddy?"],[8212,8308,"Yes."],[8308,8491,"Mommy promises I'm coming back"],[8491,8596,"with daddy, okay?"],[8687,8767,"Charlie!"],[8767,8875,"Mommy!"]],"47":[[283,450,"You looking for Dr. Charlie,"],[450,563,"Your Highness?"],[563,709,"No."],[709,921,"I was just going for a walk."],[921,1059,"You're here to propose, aren't you?"],[1155,1226,"How do you know that?"],[1226,1317,"So obvious."],[1317,1393,"All right."],[1518,1593,"Is it?"],[1605,1680,"Aren’t you going in?"],[1680,1810,"Look."],[1810,2002,"I'm scared, okay?"],[2002,2189,"Because five years ago, I also tried"],[2189,2331,"to proposed to Dr.Charlie."],[2331,2385,"And it wa -"],[2385,2444,"Your Highness!"],[2444,2502,"Your Highness."],[2548,2806,"I don't know what happened five years ago,"],[2806,2890,"but do you love her?"],[2890,2977,"Yes I do."],[2977,3190,"Then there's nothing to be afraid of."],[4654,4854,"So, how’d it go?"],[5109,5196,"She's gone."],[5201,5342,"I’ll check surveillance right away."],[5342,5522,"Don't worry."],[5522,5672,"She may have just stepped out."],[6072,6202,"Couldn't find Dr. Charlie."],[6202,6339,"All we found was her phone."],[6756,6806,"Hello."],[6806,6886,"Harry."],[6906,7111,"Something has happened to Charlie."]],"48":[[58,175,"Okay what happened?"],[175,358,"I was on the phone with Charlie and Nick,"],[358,538,"and then suddenly, a man dressed in black"],[538,638,"kidnapped her."],[663,788,"Who could it be?"],[788,1017,"Harry, you have to save her."],[1017,1322,"What you saw five years ago was just an act."],[1322,1559,"She never betrayed you. Help her."],[1559,1676,"What do you mean, an act?"],[1676,1843,"Her mother was ill."],[1843,2039,"She didn't even know who you were."],[2039,2223,"She thought she would be a burden to you"],[2223,2389,"so she asked me to fake it"],[2389,2502,"and make you leave her."],[2640,2861,"So that means that Nick is my son?"],[2869,3036,"Your Highness, you're getting a call."],[3299,3399,"Your Highness."],[3495,3674,"You ruined my plan and killed my man."],[3674,3824,"I think it's only fair"],[3824,3999,"that you pay the price too."],[4012,4129,"Okay, what do you want?"],[4141,4479,"I want you to come here alone."],[4479,4746,"And if I see anyone else,"],[4817,5059,"then your little doctor friend here"],[5059,5217,"she’ll be blown to bits."],[5509,5689,"Sir, you can't go alone."],[5689,5772,"It's too dangerous."],[5772,5889,"Listen to me."],[5889,6014,"You don't tell my father."],[6014,6164,"You don't tell anybody about this."],[6164,6348,"Nobody can find out."],[6348,6531,"But, Sir."],[7082,7303,"True to your word, Your Highness."],[7328,7536,"Let her go, let her go!"],[7645,7795,"If I kill you,"],[7795,8053,"I will certainly go down in history."],[8070,8279,"And I'm killing her with you."]],"49":[[508,713,"You okay? It’s okay."],[775,975,"Run! Harry, run!"],[975,1088,"I've seen the movies."],[1088,1192,"If you cut the wrong one,"],[1192,1276,"then we're both going to die."],[1276,1351,"Just go!"],[1351,1426,"You know what?"],[1426,1643,"Relax, okay? I know what I'm doing."],[1956,2077,"Oh, shit."],[2077,2281,"What's going on? What's wrong?"],[2356,2460,"Just go, okay."],[2460,2552,"Just leave me!"],[2552,2719,"You know what?"],[2719,2840,"There’s something I forgot to do."],[2840,3053,"What could be more urgent than this?"],[3053,3349,"Charlie."],[3428,3524,"Will you marry me?"],[3657,3782,"Stop playing around Harry."],[3782,3941,"You have to go. Just go."],[3941,4145,"I don't care if this is the last moment of my life."],[4145,4350,"I want to do this with you."],[4383,4500,"Yes."],[4500,4654,"Harry, I'll marry you."],[7628,7857,"You see,"],[7857,8053,"nothing can stop us now."],[8354,8654,"We can finally be together."],[9096,9396,"You are not allowed to have what I can't have."],[9455,9559,"Harry's mine."],[9642,9755,"No, Harry."]],"50":[[0,33,"Harry!"],[33,158,"Harry!"],[158,442,"I didn't, I didn't mean to I -"],[442,592,"It was all because of her."],[592,784,"That bitch!"],[784,1034,"It wasn't me. It wasn't me. It was her."],[1034,1121,"It was Charlie."],[1121,1217,"She did it."],[1217,1393,"She’s guilty, Harry."],[1413,1614,"David, please take him to the hospital."],[1614,1843,"Let's take him, come on!"],[2035,2235,"Dr. Charlie, can you do this?"],[2364,2444,"Yes."],[2590,2790,"Don't worry, Harry."],[2790,3015,"I promise."],[3199,3499,"Scalpel."],[4604,5000,"Harry, I just accepted your proposal."],[5000,5176,"You can't leave me now."],[5196,5518,"You haven't even met Nick yet."],[5518,5693,"I told Nick that,"],[5693,5918,"I would come back to see him with his dad."],[5989,6231,"You can't break that promise."],[6231,6473,"You’re his father."]],"51":[[166,329,"Harry?"],[329,467,"Harry, are you okay?"],[475,592,"Are your wounds hurting?"],[592,734,"Charlie."],[1105,1167,"Yeah."],[1167,1472,"It actually hurts a lot."],[1472,1572,"Right here."],[1647,1805,"Are you joking right now?"],[1926,2102,"Do you have any idea how worried"],[2102,2281,"I was about you?"],[2281,2535,"What would I have done if you died?"],[2535,2686,"What about our son?"],[2969,3157,"What did you say?"],[3407,3595,"Hey."],[3757,3920,"Charlie."],[3920,4220,"Did you say our, our son?"],[4254,4429,"Is Nick our child?"],[4537,4838,"Little Nick is our son?"],[4867,5196,"Come here."],[5939,6101,"Okay, you need to rest now."],[6101,6281,"We can't have you straining your wounds."],[6281,6410,"These are serious."],[6410,6619,"You know, Dr. Charlie, I was."],[6619,6877,"It was very mean of you to keep a"],[6877,7136,"secret like that from me."],[7161,7407,"As a consolation,"],[7407,7707,"would you help by healing my wounds?"],[8053,8199,"The nurse will take care of that."],[8199,8500,"No, no, no, I."],[8721,8867,"I only want you to do it."],[9338,9388,"Okay."],[9388,9626,"I'll, I'll take that as a yes."],[10443,10573,"Come back in three days."],[10618,10756,"Dr. Charlie?"],[10756,10952,"You know, I know you must be pretty busy"],[10952,11081,"as an ER doctor,"],[11081,11444,"so you probably don't have a boyfriend, right?"],[11507,11740,"You probably live a very dangerous"],[11740,11861,"life in the army."],[11861,12195,"So no girlfriend,"],[12245,12449,"right?"],[12545,12816,"Dr. Charlie,"],[12816,13104,"I know that you must have such a"],[13104,13213,"busy schedule,"],[13213,13430,"so I'm going to assume"],[13430,13651,"that you haven’t found a husband yet,"],[13651,13730,"right?"],[13792,14072,"And you, as a soldier"],[14072,14230,"with such a dangerous lifestyle,"],[14230,14422,"I'm gonna assume that you haven't"],[14422,14589,"had a wife yet."]],"52":[[291,554,"Nick, even with your dad here now,"],[554,792,"remember that Uncle Gavin is still your favorite."],[792,838,"Okay?"],[838,996,"Yes, Uncle Gavin."],[1113,1263,"It's Daddy!"],[1559,1814,"He just told me that I was his favorite"],[1814,1947,"and the second his dad comes,"],[1947,2093,"he just runs straight into his arms."],[2093,2139,"Yeah."],[2139,2348,"He told me yesterday that he missed mommy,"],[2348,2581,"but I haven't even gotten a hug yet."],[2765,2898,"What are you two talking about?"],[2973,3107,"I'm not telling you."],[3249,3574,"Well, you know, I think that Uncle Gavin,"],[3574,3728,"is going to drive us home."],[5005,5155,"Mom, the doctors said the surgery"],[5155,5313,"went well."],[5313,5501,"You're going to be recovered soon."],[5505,5630,"You've just come back from such"],[5630,5930,"a tough place and you've worked so hard."],[5930,6093,"Don't worry."],[6093,6289,"The people that Harry sent,"],[6289,6485,"are taking such good care of me."],[6585,6856,"I heard everything from Gavin."],[6856,7161,"And it was my fault before, but,"],[7161,7336,"Harry's a good man."],[7349,7607,"You two take care of each other now, okay?"],[7774,7878,"We will."],[8041,8137,"I love you."],[8137,8337,"I love you too."],[8458,8633,"You’re a father now?"],[8696,8983,"Dr. charlie’s son, is your son?"],[8983,9138,"She only ever loved me."],[9209,9351,"And who was it that said Charlie"],[9351,9426,"couldn't be trusted?"],[9426,9676,"And I only ever loved her."],[9768,9951,"What are you going to do about your father?"]],"53":[[45,162,"How was school today, baby?"],[162,246,"Great!"],[246,342,"Good, what did you make?"],[342,487,"I made a lot of drawings."],[487,588,"Oh, I love this one."],[588,650,"Greetings."],[650,775,"Miss Charlie."],[775,930,"My name is Chuck."],[930,1163,"I'm an aide to His Majesty."],[1201,1376,"The King would like to request"],[1376,1926,"the presence of you and little Nick."],[2481,2752,"So."],[2752,3011,"This is Harry's son, Nick."],[3019,3219,"Your Majesty, why did you bring us here?"],[3307,3566,"Well, Charlie,"],[3566,3762,"if you leave Harry"],[3762,4166,"and leave Nick with us,"],[4483,4650,"the money is yours."],[5263,5522,"Charlie."],[5522,5734,"Charlie."],[5922,6335,"So, this is Harry's son, Nick."],[6385,6473,"Your Majesty,"],[6473,6660,"what are you planning to do?"],[6956,7111,"Just like I imagined."],[7111,7378,"Can I really protect Nick from the King?"]],"54":[[20,175,"Your Majesty, I don't want the money."],[262,533,"I love Harry, and I love our son."],[533,784,"I will never leave them."],[888,1013,"Wait!"],[1030,1176,"Charlie."],[1176,1292,"Please sit."],[1730,2052,"Charlie, you misunderstood."],[2052,2431,"I'm not here to take Nick away from you."],[2460,2798,"This money is a token of gratitude."],[2798,3178,"From me, as Nick's Grandfather."],[3178,3478,"And for you raising him alone all these years."],[3478,3674,"I'm sure it was hard."],[3816,4008,"Your Majesty, this is too much."],[4008,4295,"No! No."],[4295,4562,"As a Prince,"],[4562,4813,"Harry represents not only himself,"],[4813,5125,"but the entire Royal family."],[5125,5296,"That's why I always wanted him to marry"],[5296,5563,"a woman of his same status."],[5563,5843,"But,"],[5843,6143,"as Harry's father,"],[6143,6381,"I only truly want him to be happy."],[6406,6890,"I saw how much he's loved you over the years."],[6890,7098,"And now I see that you love him too."],[7148,7319,"So I won't stand in your way."],[7349,7494,"I just wish you both happiness."],[7615,7799,"Mom, don't cry."],[7887,8091,"Grandpa’s giving us a blessing."],[8245,8370,"Come here, Nick."],[8370,8550,"Give Grandpa a hug."],[9213,9355,"Charlie, are you okay?"],[9667,9826,"Hey, dad."],[9826,10005,"Just so we're clear."],[10005,10218,"Charlie is the love of my life, okay?"],[10218,10356,"How dare you insult her like that?"],[10372,10685,"No Harry, he wasn't insulting me."],[10685,10940,"He was giving us a blessing."],[10973,11065,"Really?"],[11169,11428,"Grandpa, don't be mad at daddy."],[11428,11632,"Oh. Well, okay,"],[11632,11803,"if you say so, Nicky."],[11803,12007,"I won't be mad anymore."],[12041,12157,"Charlie."],[12354,12662,"How about we make it official?"],[12733,13079,"As your husband and as Nick's father."],[13142,13196,"What?"],[13196,13371,"The wedding."],[13371,13605,"When do you want to have our wedding?"],[14126,14218,"How about now?"],[14218,14360,"Okay."],[14360,14501,"All right."],[14606,14743,"You know that I have been"],[14743,14939,"waiting for you to say the word."],[15286,15340,"Yes?"],[15340,15523,"Come here."],[15671,15708,"So..."],[15819,15915,"Hey! Come here."],[16045,16216,"Good job buddy."],[16408,16745,"Mommy and Daddy are getting married!"]]}